Specifically, packages/executor-worktree adapts Cyrus's GitService
worktree lifecycle (worktree create/teardown, base-branch resolution,
and the sanitizeBranchName helper) and follows the SDK-to-activity
mapping approach of Cyrus's AgentSessionManager for the runner adapters'
normalised trace envelope. The adapted code has been substantially
rewritten and stripped of Cyrus-core coupling; the original licence and
attribution are preserved here per Apache-2.0 section 4.
